    "The communication attenuation caused by speech, represented by r 1, involves complex factors, making it difficult to evaluate directly.",
    "To assess the impact of r 1, each RQ compares two input sets: the colloquial input set S col.1, which includes r 1 and is based on human speech, and the ideal input set S ide.1, which excludes r 1 and is generated by the LLM.",
    "The experiment aims to quantitatively evaluate the outputs of three newly introduced processes in the proposed method: automatic service name generation, automatic keyword extraction, and upcycling case search.",
